name: AhoyNave
summary: The AhoyNave iOS SDK is built to provide seamless integration of Navigation along with Map functionalities into your app
description:
The features of AhoyNave are
Display a Map with zoom and pan functionality
Add markers to the map
Add a polyline
Add a polygon
Load custom themes(Day/Night) etc
Navigate from source to destination
Restricting the route
